race.description: Tabtouch - Have You Got The Touch Hcp (C1)
race.comment: FIRE THE LOT (2) looks hard to beat here fresh. Showed plenty of ability on debut at Pinjarra over the winter with a determined win in what has proven a hot form race. Given plenty of time and two easy trials. Will ride the speed here and should go close. SKYTALKER (1) looks the danger fresh. Form is better than it looks and good for this level. Resumed last time in with a placing at Northam and has placed 3/5 while fresh. Fitter for a trial and won't get a better chance to return to winning form. QUICK AS SILVER (4) was a winner three back then not far away last two. Will be on speed and with the claim is a definite winning chance. ORKNEY LAD (6) was a maiden winner in easier company last time when led throughout. Tougher assignment but will take catching. BOSISTO (3) is going better than it looks and has the blinkers added. Worth including.
